A moment where Indian cinema takes over the world.

We are honoured to announce that #Homebound makes its way to the official selection at the 78th edition of the Festival De Cannes in the 'Un Certain Regard' category.

Our hearts are full and we can't wait to show you all this journey on the big screens!🎬

Written by Neeraj Ghaywan & @gogoroy
Screenplay by Neeraj Ghaywan
Dialogues by Neeraj Ghaywan, @vidushak & @shreedharindia

@ishaankhatter @vishaljethwa06 @karanjohar @adarpoonawalla @apoorva1972 @somenmishra @neeraj.ghaywan @marijkedesouza @melitatoscan
